      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03-ngs021.m4a",
      "text": "……分かりました\n私、少し弱気になっていました",
      "startTime": 156.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03-ngs022.m4a",
      "text": "役に立てることがあるのかなって",
      "startTime": 160.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03-ngs023.m4a",
      "text": "でも、もう大丈夫そうです\n今日のライブも頑張ってきます！",
      "startTime": 165.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "（ライブは盛況のうちに終わった）\n（みんな力を出しきったのか、床に座り込んでいる）",
      "startTime": 173.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "（今日もみんな、よく頑張ってくれたな）\n（特に渚は、心なしか普段より堂々としていた気がする）",
      "startTime": 180.73333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03-ngs024.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、琴乃ちゃん。今日のライブ\n凄く盛り上がったね。私、楽しかったよ",
      "startTime": 188.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03-ngs025.m4a",
      "text": "実は私、ライブの前、心配なことがあったんだ\n……何って？　ふふ、内緒だよ",
      "startTime": 198.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03-ngs026.m4a",
      "text": "でもステージに立って、琴乃ちゃんと一緒に歌って\nダンスをしてたら、どこかに飛んでいっちゃった",
      "startTime": 207.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03-ngs027.m4a",
      "text": "だからありがとう、琴乃ちゃん\nこれからも月ストで一緒に頑張っていこうね",
      "startTime": 213.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_03-koh018.m4a",
      "text": "（……そろそろ帰る時間だけど）\n（もう少しだけ、そっとしておくか……）",
      "startTime": 220.6,
